Subject: Re: Smartcard-Logon and NTLM-Backward Compatability


You might want to use a SPNEGO module on your Tomcat server. Please
see http://bofriis.dk/index.html?http://bofriis.dk/spnego/qa.html and
http://www.vintela.com/resources/topics/spnego/ to d/l the SPNEGO
module.

SPNEGO will allow your Tomcat server to participate in a AD Kerberos
envinronment, just like any other server that understand Kerberos
Tickets.

